stituting In my t under correction a program a conducive to increased pros all times and calculated there to to impede but to promote ty now I believe included in igory are The Wagner btlle for the re Uif of unemployment Public work including in land waterways and a public building Conservation and control of tlpn of courts or equity in certain cbsee Prevention of the inflation Mid deflation of credit If Sixth A better balanced distribu tion f national Income ifgeventh The tariff Chides Party LeMers JThe statement of the seven Demo cratic leaders promising cooperation with the administration in the new Congress and acceptance of the offer by Republican leaders suggests to Ben asPr Shipstead that the leaders of both parties are atlast tempted to embrace OBorge Washingtons opinion that the spirit of party serves always to dis trict the public councils and enfeeble tire public administration SVith sarcasm suggesting amusement BJflpstead welcomed their conversion lnstead of following Washington we today have seemingly to a large extent submerged our loyalty to"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2020-09-15T07:39:55.701Z", "group": ["ndnp/dlc-2018_2019", "library-of-congress-washington-dc-awardee-7"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83045462/1930-11-16/ed-1/?sp=2", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_oliver_ver01:data:sn83045462:00280600556:1930111601:0099/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=263&w=204", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_oliver_ver01:data:sn83045462:00280600556:1930111601:0099/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=526&w=409", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_oliver_ver01:data:sn83045462:00280600556:1930111601:0099/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1052&w=819", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/dlc/batch_dlc_oliver_ver01/data/sn83045462/00280600556/1930111601/0099.xml&format